        <doc title="TerminateSession" xml:lang="en">Terminates an active session. A &lt;code&gt;TerminateSession&lt;/code&gt; call on a session that is already inactive (for example, in a &lt;code&gt;FAILED&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;TERMINATED&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;TERMINATING&lt;/code&gt; state) succeeds but has no effect. Calculations running in the session when &lt;code&gt;TerminateSession&lt;/code&gt; is called are forcefully stopped, but may display as &lt;code&gt;FAILED&lt;/code&gt; instead of &lt;code&gt;STOPPED&lt;/code&gt;.</doc>
